        <div class="inner">
            <ul class="icons">
                <li><a target="_blank" href="https://www.instagram.com/vuongee/"
                       class="icon brands style2 fa-instagram"><span class="label">Instagram</span></a></li>
                <li><a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/vuongp/"
                       class="icon brands style2 fa-linkedin"><span class="label">LinkedIn</span></a></li>
                <li><a target="_blank" href="mailto:h.vuongpham@gmail.com" class="icon style2 fa-envelope"><span
                        class="label">Email</span></a></li>
            </ul>
            <p>Vudi preview 2025, Design: <a href="https://html5up.net" target="_blank">HTML5 UP</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>